### Search all items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/search

###

### Search lost electronics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/search?type=lost&category=Electronics

###

### Search by keyword
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/search?keyword=phone

###

### Get nearby items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/nearby?lat=30.0444&lng=31.2357&radius=5

###

### Get matches for item
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/ITEM_ID_HERE/matches
